membantumu di sini, bung.

92
00:09:26,642 --> 00:09:28,186
Aku harus mencari Ricky Verona.

93
00:09:28,227 --> 00:09:31,147
- Bagaimana aku tahu
di mana Ricky Verona? - Ya, ya.

94
00:09:31,522 --> 00:09:32,732
